-- MOVES-Wolfgang Mantke joins GFT's risk management practice
-- 
-- Thu Dec 18, 2014 06:47AM EST
-- None



Dec 18 (Reuters) - GFT Technologies AG <GFTG.DE>, a provider of advisory, consulting and software to the investment banking industry, has appointed Wolfgang Mantke a principal consultant in its risk management practice.

Mantke joins from the Royal Bank of Scotland <RBS.L> in London, where he spent three years as a market risk manager in the investment banking division, GFT said.